  <description><![CDATA[<p>The modern L'Eclose Apart-Hotel is great option for those looking for modern accommodation in <a data-udi="umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497" href="/{localLink:umb://document/acff50eb9ad84862a464f68b551bc497}" title="Alpe d'Huez">Alpe d'Huez</a>. The building has a great mix of modern and traditional architecture, which has taken inspiration from its surroundings in the resort and mountains.</p>
<h2>Perfect Location </h2>
<p>The hotel is located right at the bottom of the ski slope, giving you convenient and easy access to the sunny slopes of Alpe d'Huez. It's also right by the ski lifts so you will have really easy access to the slopes of Grand Domaine.</p>
<h2>Modern Facilities</h2>
<p>There's a heated indoor swimming pool surrounded by windows to look out at the slopes. As well as a fitness room, hammam, sauna and massage treatment cabins. For the children there's a paddling pool and entertainment area, then for the adults the hotel has a bar area. </p>
<p>If you are looking for a self-catering apartment then <a data-udi="umb://document/59113056e60f4520b083d59a6650f0e3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59113056e60f4520b083d59a6650f0e3}" title="L'Eclose Apartments" data-anchor="#">L'Eclose Apartments</a> are a great new option, and in the same building. </p>]]></description>
