  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double rooms</strong> are approximately 22m² and sleep up to two people. The bed can be made up as a double or two single beds, please advise at time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>Junior suites</strong> are approximately 33m² and sleep four people, in a double bed and sofa bed. There's a bedroom with double bed and a living room with a pull-out sofa bed, and a bathroom with a separate toilet. </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kitchenette with ceramic hob, fridge, microwave/grill, dishwasher, coffee machine, kettle, toaster</li>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Bathroom with bath and towel dryer</li>
<li>Bed linen</li>
<li>Beds made on arrival</li>
<li>Daily cleaning </li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Baby kit included cot, stairgate and highchair, please request when booking</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
